@node pre "Prefomated blocks"

 Font size (-fsize) option @{b}doesn't@{ub} work with preformated blocks.
 
 With preformated blocks INetBrowser can display spaces, tabulators
 and end lines characters like in ASCI (txt) mode.

@endnode